<br>
Phreezin dear your suffocating me and plz quit squeezing me so hard. I'm still hurting a bit.   As Phreezin lets up on his bear hug.  Rhapsodey looks over to her Sword sister Reoki.  ,&quot;excellent work as always Sis.  But next time would you plz put on a  leash on my  Dear Husband he's  trying to squeeze me in two and I really could go without my chest being Squeezed down into my stomach and up into my head.&quot;<br>
<br>
As Rhapsodey carefully sits down by Phreezin and wraps herself back in the blankets and lays her head against his shoulder.  ,&quot;Blast what happened?   I feel colder than the time I went Skin diving in the waters of Everfrost to Recover those bodies of those young warriors that were thrown in after they were killed.&quot;  She  takes the cup of soup that Reoki hands her and quietly drinks it.   After finishing it she looks at the sky and offers a small song of Thanks.<br>
<br>
After a short bit she looks at her Sister and Husband.  ,&quot;I think it is time that we payed my Dear Father a visit once I have recovered a bit that is.  Something is very wrong here and ive had enough of this.  But  I think that you two had best gather us some friends to go along.  I keep sensing necromantic magic as if we are being watched.  And if this is my father using it something is very very Wrong.<br>
Rhapsodey returns to watching the fire burn and as she does the fire  that burns in her eyes  begins to burn brighter as her determination becomes more set to see this game to an end.<br>
