<br>
Reoki steps forward,&quot;yes I am here Wolfgar&quot;  An obviously exhasuted young warrior steps forth and offers a rolled Parchment to REoki.<br>
<br>
Reoki unrolls the Parchment and begins to read.<br>
<br>
Reoki<br>
If you are wise you will return our Daughter to us immediately.  If you fail to do so we will have to assume that you have fallen under the dark magic of Phreezin and will be forced to take action against you and your people who have obviosly become influnced as well.<br>
