&quot;ok. You'll head for the druid ring in NK and get to freeport. There must be someone round there. I'll search out karanas and if I dont find anyone I'll get TP'ed to...GFAY maybe&quot; states Canute. &quot;Fine by me&quot; says Cogito, happy to get as far away from the lurking evil as possible.<br>
The two break up camp and Canute renews their sow.<br>
Neither being good swimmers, Canute also casts levitate on the pair before they travel on at a frantic pace.<br>
