 &quot;I'm am going to scout the area for other assasins.  Rhapsodey I think you need to read this missive i recieved from your mother yesterday.  Something is not right here.  Your mother doesn't tlak or write this way as far as I can remeber.  Mayby you can find out what is wronge.   I am also sending a spirit message to ALL the shamans of the northern tribes.  They must be warned.&quot; Reoki states.<br>
