<br>
As his Lifeless body falls from the mount the female dark elf warror jumps back with an oath.  As she turns drawing her weapon an arrow takes her through the leg the heavy war arrow head breaking her leg and the pain causing her to pass out.  A female Barbarian warrior step from behind a tree Heavy war bow in hand.  Weapons protruding around her like a halo.  She slow and carefully walks forward arrow noked ready to fire another shot.  Kicking the weapons  away from the dark elves.  As the Black wolf comes up from Behind.  She looks up as it aproaches.  She speaks to the wolf.  &quot;YOu were Right Jaelynn  their are dark elves here for me to kill.  I see they have captured one of my Brother can you return him home for me while I go see what thes dark skined scum bags are up to.&quot;  The wolves speaks.  &quot;what do you intend to do with her Maith?&quot;  Nothing much Jaey im going to wake her up and ask her a few questions then im going to add her pretty white hair to my collection of dark elf scalps.  The normal for me since that day so long ago that you saved me from them:&quot;  Jaey shakes her head.  &quot;Maybee  I shouldnt of asked&quot; says Jaey as she and Khaldorn and the mount disapear to surefall Glade.<br>
